thread.title: clyde simpson

author: clyde simpson
title: clyde simpson
text: From booking to drop off was first class. I booked on line in Australia for a seven day adventure in New Zealand's North Island. A free call at Auckland Airport upon arrival was all that was needed to start our journey. The vehicle and paperwork were ready and so were we. A few formalities and we were on our way in a brand new Nissan X-Trail. Approx 2000k/m and seven days later we handed the vehicle back and flew home. The staff were so helpful and courteous in every sense of the word and the vehicles presentation was faultless. I would have no hesitation in recommending OMEGA rental cars to anybody.
